		<p>Mr. Crane raised his eyebrows at me but didn't say anything.</p>

		<p>As I collected some clothes and toiletries -- all that I would need for my
		next few lonely nights at Donny's empty apartment -- I wondered if Mr. Crane
		knew more than he was letting on.</p>

		<h2 align="center">Le Freres Heureux</h2>

		<p>"I just don't know what to do, Doctor Crane.  We've never fought like this
