		appreciate your sister's presence.  It's hard for her, too.  She may feel at
		this early stage that you're encroaching on her territory.  Just let her
		know, Nancy, every second how much you value your relationship."</p>

		<p>He stopped and raised his head, waiting a bit.  There were some sniffles on
		the line, but no Nancy.  "Nancy?"</p>

