		certainly has a way.  He'd made poor Nancy cry.</p>

		<p>"But did it help you, Nancy?"  He sounded a bit desperate.  I think, right
		now, he needed to feel that his story had helped someone, even if he felt
		his  relationship with Niles was currently in tatters.</p>

		<p>"Oh, yes, Doctor Crane!  In fact, I think I'm going to take Samantha to
